    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission are operational and it gets from A to B consistently, there are visible signs of wear including some scratches on the exterior and minor staining on the interior upholstery. It has been maintained adequately to keep it running, though a buyer should expect some upcoming minor maintenance typical for a car of this age and mileage. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
