    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this masterfully preserved specimen, currently held in exemplary condition. This vehicle exhibits no discernible wear; every surface\u2014from the flawless coachwork to the pristine interior appointments\u2014reflects a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. Rigorously inspected and maintained to an exacting standard, this motorcar offers an uncompromising experience for the most discerning enthusiast. A rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in its finest possible state.",
      "price": 48950.0,
