    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to check out this absolute beauty! It\u2019s been kept in incredible shape and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, so it\u2019s super clean and ready for a new home. If you're looking for that perfect, like-new feel without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
