    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, maintained to exacting standards. The 13B-REW power plant retains its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, delivering a seamless boost transition across the power band. This specimen features a pristine chassis with factory-spec forged aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a perfectly balanced 50:50 weight distribution. Mechanical integrity is verified by exceptional, uniform compression across all rotor faces. The drivetrain remains unmodified, featuring the original short-throw five-speed manual gearbox and Torsen limited-slip differential. Every vacuum line, heat shield, and electrical connector is in concours-level condition, showing zero signs of the thermal degradation common in the FD platform.",
